import React from 'react'
import { Box } from '@mui/material';
import Header from '../Header';
import { Form } from 'react-bootstrap'

function LogTransaction() {
    return (
        <Box m='20px'>
            <Box display={'flex'} justifyContent={'space-between'} alignItems={'center'}>
                <Header title={'Log Transaction'} subtitle={'Log an expense here'} />
            </Box>

            <Form>
                <Form.Group className='mb-3' controlId='testformgroup'>
                    <Form.Label>Who is it for?</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type='number' placeholder='$-.--' size='lg' />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group className='mb-3' controlId='testformgroup'>
                    <Form.Label>Category</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type='number' placeholder='$-.--' />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group className='mb-3' controlId='testformgroup'>
                    <Form.Label>Price</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type='number' placeholder='$-.--' />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group className='mb-3' controlId='testformgroup'>
                    <Form.Label>Description</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type='number' placeholder='$-.--' />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Select className='mb-3' controlId='testformgroup'>
                    <Form.Label>Who paid?</Form.Label>
                    <option>yl</option>
                    <option>en</option>
                    <option>dj</option>
                    <option>chubby</option>
                </Form.Select>
            </Form>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default LogTransaction;
